%% Diagram: Decision tree for choosing event-driven vs request-driven and which patterns to layer on
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TD
    Start([New service or<br/>integration point]) --> Q1{Strong consistency<br/>and immediate feedback?}
    Q1 -- Yes --> Req[Request-driven<br/>HTTP / gRPC]
    Q1 -- No --> Q2{Multiple consumers<br/>or independent scaling?}
    Q2 -- No --> Req
    Q2 -- Yes --> Events[Event-driven via broker]

    Events --> A1{Audit trail or<br/>temporal queries?}
    A1 -- Yes --> ES["+ Event sourcing<br/>(see deep-dive)"]
    A1 -- No --> A2{Read patterns differ<br/>significantly from writes?}
    ES --> A2
    A2 -- Yes --> CQRS[+ CQRS]
    A2 -- No --> Sagas{Distributed workflow?}
    CQRS --> Sagas
    Sagas -- 2-3 steps --> Choreo[Choreography]
    Sagas -- 5+ steps --> Orch[Orchestration]
    Sagas -- No --> Done([Single-service handler])

    style Req fill:#dae8fc,stroke:#6c8ebf
    style Events fill:#fff2cc,stroke:#d6b656
    style ES fill:#d5e8d4,stroke:#82b366
    style CQRS fill:#d5e8d4,stroke:#82b366
    style Orch fill:#f8cecc,stroke:#b85450
    style Choreo fill:#e1d5e7,stroke:#9673a6
